(17, '一个免费的在线表格转换工具——TableConvert', 1582609867, '转载', 5, 17, 'upload/article/20200225\\672cc2a27b3b253c3beb48135c341383.jpg', 'TableConvert 是一个可以在线转换表格的在线web工具', 'TableConvert 是一个可以在线转换表格的在线web工具', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(177, 177, 193); font-size: 18px;">TableConvert 是一个可以在线转换表格的在线web工具，支持 Markdown 表格、CSV、JSON、XML、YAML、SQL、HTML 表格、Excel 和 LaTeX 表格，并且还内嵌了一个表格编辑器，像微软的 Excel 一样编辑，使用非常方便。</span></p><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25rem; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" -webkit-font-smoothing:="" border-left:="" 3px="" solid="" padding-left:="" color:="" white-space:="" background-color:="">网站名称：<a href="https://tableconvert.com/" target="_blank">Table Convert Online</a></h2><p><br style="text-align: left;"/></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.125rem; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" -webkit-font-smoothing:="" position:="" padding-left:="" color:="" white-space:="" background-color:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">如何使用</span></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" background-color:="" color:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">下面以 Excel 转换成 Markdown 表格为例<span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">步骤1.</span>&nbsp;打开 TableConvert，单击菜单栏中的</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Import</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">按钮，切换到</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Excel</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">选项卡。在导入窗口中，你可以看到如下提示：</span></p><blockquote style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 2rem 0px; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" -webkit-font-smoothing:="" position:="" padding:="" 0px="" border-left:="" 5px="" solid="" color:="" white-space:="" background-color:=""><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(177, 177, 193) !important; text-align: left;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 18px;">Paste your cells from Excel, Numbers, Google Docs or Browser table</span></p></blockquote><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; white-space: normal; word-break: break-all; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" background-color:="" color:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">步骤2.</span>&nbsp;如上所述，从 Excel（或其他电子表格程序）复制一系列单元格并将其粘贴到文本框中，单击</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Import data</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">按钮。<br style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"/><span style="font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;">步骤3.</span>&nbsp;现在，从 Excel 复制的内容已导入网站并自动转换为 Markdown 表格，你只需要确保在输出区域中选择的选项卡是</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Markdown</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">。<br style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;"/>单击</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Copy</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">按钮将结果复制到剪贴板。单击</span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, " liberation="" courier="" font-size:="" color:="" word-break:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">Dowuload</span></code><span style="font-size: 18px;">按钮将 Markdown 文件下载到本地。拿到对应 Excel 表格的 Markdown 后，可以直接在文档中使用该文本。</span></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.125rem; text-align: left;" sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" -webkit-font-smoothing:="" position:="" padding-left:="" color:="" white-space:="" background-color:=""><span style="font-size: 18px;">功能列表</span></h3><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 45px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: " sf="" pro="" pingfang="" lantinghei="" microsoft="" hiragino="" sans="" wenquanyi="" micro="" white-space:="" background-color:="" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">转换，编辑和生成 Markdown 表格、CSV、JSON、XML、YAML、SQL、HTML 表格、Excel 和 LaTeX 表格</span></p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">可视化表格创建器</span></p></li><li><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">类似于 Excel 的表格编辑器，同时支持键盘和鼠标操作</span></p></li><